  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13108016/lapland-guide-couples-5-x900.jpg" alt="CouplesLapland1" data-udi="umb://media/eda22e96bb614609b53f66de422b55ae" /></p>
<p>Step off the plane and into the glistening white snow under a starry night sky and start your romantic getaway to Lapland.</p>
<p>There is so much that makes Lapland one of the most romantic destinations you can visit as a couple.</p>
<p>Spend your days soaking in the majestic wildlife that roam the tree-lined frozen lakes or make the most of Finland's love for Saunas and enjoy a spa day.</p>
<p>Choose to spend the evenings wrapped up warm together in front of the fire in your cosy cabin for two or stare at the never-ending stars in the night sky (possibly with a glimpse of the Northern Lights).</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">View Lapland holiday deals</a></p>
<h2>Romantic Lapland holidays</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3>Romantic ways to spend the day:</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108015/lapland-guide-couples-2-x900.jpg" alt="CouplesLapland2" data-udi="umb://media/1c875e4bd4894ba49cc737426853b474" /></p>
<p>There is something special about the peaceful surroundings in <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a>, no more so than when gliding through the scenery on a horse or husky drawn sleigh. Cuddle up together under a blanket and soak up the beautiful sights - from majestic, snow laden trees, ice covered lakes to the mesmerising Northern Lights above.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719" href="/{localLink:umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719}" title="Reindeer Rides" class="c-btn">View Reindeer safari</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec}" title="Husky Rides" class="c-btn">View Husky Safari</a></p>
<p>Book a unique experience for you and your partner and visit the Ice Village &amp; Hotel. This mesmerising village provides the perfect setting for a romantic day out - wander through the lit up ice sculptures and ice-wall art as you make your way to the Ice Hotel. Here you can either enjoy the ice bar with your drinks served from ice glasses or dine in the amazingly ice sculpted restaurant.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869}" title="Ice Activities" class="c-btn">View Ice Activities</a></p>
<p>The Finnish love a Sauna and you will find them at nearly every hotel, apartment or log cabin. Why not spend the day relaxing together at a hotel spa and make the most of all the great facilities on offer. There are plenty of hotels with amazing spa facilities across the 3 resorts of Lapland. We highly recommend Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel and Levi Hotel Spa, both perfect for a full spa day offering facilities such as multiple swimming pools, saunas, steam rooms and hot tubs.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel" class="c-btn">View Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec}" title="Levi Hotel Spa" class="c-btn">View Levi Hotel Spa</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: left;">When to visit Lapland on a couples holiday</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108017/lapland-guide-couples-6-x900.jpg" alt="CouplesLapland3" data-udi="umb://media/b6e552ea3e2a419197ba545f82d7f6dd" /></p>
<p>Lapland certainly feels like a romantic destination in the winter, however there are certain times of year that make a holiday here feel extra special.</p>
<p>Choose to visit at <a data-udi="umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2}" title="Lapland holidays at Christmas">Christmas</a> and enjoy a cosy, calm escape together with festive feasts, Christmas markets and town centres glowing with lights and Christmas themed decorations to enjoy.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2}" title="Lapland holidays at Christmas">New Year's Eve</a> adds a touch of romance to your trip to Lapland - enjoy a firework display like no other, and perhaps nature's own natural light display of the Northern Lights. A midnight kiss under the skies of Lapland will be one to remember.</p>
<p>There is also something quite special about visiting Lapland in February, the ideal escape for Valentines or to make a birthday extra special. A true place for romance, where you enjoy delicious candlelit dinners, relaxing and quiet saunas and beds that lay beneath a canopy of stars. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">View Lapland deals</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Romantic stays under the stars</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108019/lapland-guide-couples-3-x900.jpg" alt="LaplandCouples4" data-udi="umb://media/6b9d41800dd0482c8baf8f241ae1475d" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c09f725698b346fcbc4cc54b08aee832" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c09f725698b346fcbc4cc54b08aee832}" title="Design Hotel Levi">Design Hotel Levi</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a> is a 5* rated, brand new hotel with bedrooms furnished to a high standard, offering deluxe rooms and suites. There is free access to Spa Water World on the site complex.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c}" title="Yllas Saaga Apartments">Yllas Saaga Apartments</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a> are 4.5* rated, modern in build and design. Offering self-catering for full privacy in your own space with a slope side location for those who are keen skiers or snowboarders. There is a sauna as well as free access to Yllas Saaga Hotel’s spa.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77}" title="Star Arctic Hotel">Star Arctic Glass cubes</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a> offer a once in a lifetime night under stars in your own private cabin with a panoramic heated glass window and roof plus sauna. You can either self-cater here or select the half-board option.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">View Lapland resorts</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Lapland short breaks</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13095240/inghams-lapland-adobestock_253760004.jpeg" alt="LaplandShortBreaks" data-udi="umb://media/200a5163f26a4fc39606efddf824b731" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b}" title="Lapland Short Breaks" class="c-btn" data-="">View short breaks</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Northern Lights holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108020/lapland-guide-couples-7-500x500.jpg" alt="NorthernLights" data-udi="umb://media/faa5b8fb2222480288c604c36bb42024" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights" class="c-btn" data-="">View holiday options</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Lapland at Christmas</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13098868/santa-and-sleigh-500x500.jpg" alt="SantaAtChristmas" data-udi="umb://media/96bedb9caab8468d96fa1370bbac4297" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2}" title="Lapland holidays at Christmas" class="c-btn" data-="">View Christmas in Lapland</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
